Package: oxen-storage-server
Architecture: any
Depends: oxend, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: oxen-service-node
Description: Oxen storage server
 This package contains the Oxen storage server component of a Oxen service
 node.  This package requires a running oxend configured as a service node; the
 default configuration is suitable for the oxend configuration set up by the
 oxen-service-node package, but it is possible to configure manually via the
 /etc/oxen/storage.conf file.

Package: loki-storage-server
Architecture: all
Section: oldlibs
Depends: oxen-storage-server, ${misc:Depends}
Description: transitional package
 This is a transitional package. It can safely be removed.
